线段树

import java.util.function.*;

public class NumArray{

    private SegmentTree<Integer> segTree;

    public NumArray(int[] nums) {
        if (nums.length>0) {
            Integer[] data=new Integer[nums.length];
            for (int i=0;i<nums.length;i++) {
                data[i]=nums[i];
            }
            segTree = new SegmentTree<Integer>(data,(a,b)->a+b);
        }
    }
    
    public void update(int i, int val) {
        segTree.update(i,val);
    }
    
    public int sumRange(int i, int j) {
        return segTree.searchRange(i,j);
    }
}

class SegmentTree<E>{
    
    private E[] data;

    private E[] tree;

    private BiFunction<E,E,E> function;

    public SegmentTree(E[] arr,BiFunction<E,E,E> function){
        data = (E[]) new Object[arr.length];
        this.function=function;
        System.arraycopy(arr,0,data,0,arr.length);
        tree = (E[]) new Object[4*arr.length];
        buildSegmentTree(0,0,arr.length-1);
    }

    //根据传入的BiFuction构建线段树
    private void buildSegmentTree(int index,int left,int right){
        if (left==right) {
            tree[index] =data[right];
            return;
        }
        int leftIndex=leftChild(index);
        int rightIndex=rightChild(index);
        int mid=left+(right-left)/2;
        buildSegmentTree(leftIndex,left,mid);
        buildSegmentTree(rightIndex,mid+1,right);
        //区间数据和,根据业务需求来
        tree[index]=function.apply(tree[leftIndex],tree[rightIndex]);
    }

    //范围搜索
    public E searchRange(int left,int right){
        return searchRange(0,0,data.length-1,left,right);
    }

    private E searchRange(int rootIndex,int left,int right,int targetLeft,int targetRight){
        if (targetLeft == left && targetRight == right) {
            return tree[rootIndex];
        }
        int mid=left+(right-left)/2;
        if (targetLeft>mid) {
            return searchRange(rightChild(rootIndex),mid+1,right,targetLeft,targetRight);
        }
        if (targetRight<=mid) {
            return searchRange(leftChild(rootIndex),left,mid,targetLeft,targetRight);
        }
        return function.apply(searchRange(leftChild(rootIndex),left,mid,targetLeft,mid),searchRange(rightChild(rootIndex),mid+1,right,mid+1,targetRight));
    }


    public void update(int index,E e){
        if (index<0 || index>=data.length) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("index illegal");
        }
        update(0,0,data.length-1,index,e);
    }

    public void update(int rootIndex,int left,int right,int targetIndex,E e){
        if (left == right) {
            tree[rootIndex]=e;
            return;
        }
        int mid=left+(right-left)/2;
        if (targetIndex<=mid) {
            update(leftChild(rootIndex),left,mid,targetIndex,e);
        }else{
            update(rightChild(rootIndex),mid+1,right,targetIndex,e);
        }
        tree[rootIndex]=function.apply(tree[leftChild(rootIndex)],tree[rightChild(rootIndex)]);
    }

    //左孩子
    private int leftChild(int index){
        return index*2+1;
    }

    //右孩子
    private int rightChild(int index){
        return index*2+2;
    }
}

## 代码：

树状数组：

class BIT:
    def __init__(self, nums):

        self.BIT_arr = [0] * (len(nums) + 1)
        # O(nlogn)
        # for i in range(len(nums)):
        #     self.updata(i, nums[i])
        # O(n)
        for i in range(len(nums)):
            self.BIT_arr[i + 1] = nums[i]
        for i in range(1, len(self.BIT_arr)):
            j = i + (i & -i)
            if j < len(self.BIT_arr):
                self.BIT_arr[j] += self.BIT_arr[i]

    def updata(self, i, delta):
        i += 1
        while i < len(self.BIT_arr):
            self.BIT_arr[i] += delta
            i += (i & (-i))

    def prefix(self, i):
        i += 1
        res = 0
        while i > 0:
            res += self.BIT_arr[i]
            i -= (i & (-i))
        return res
class NumArray:

    def __init__(self, nums):
        self.nums = nums
        self.tree = BIT(nums)

    def update(self, i: int, val: int) -> None:
        self.tree.updata(i, val - self.nums[i])
        self.nums[i] = val

    def sumRange(self, i: int, j: int) -> int:
        return self.tree.prefix(j) - self.tree.prefix(i - 1)

线段树：

class NumArray:

    def __init__(self, nums):
        self.l = len(nums)
        self.tree = [0] * self.l + nums
        for i in range(self.l - 1, 0, -1):
            self.tree[i] = self.tree[i << 1] + self.tree[i << 1 | 1]

    def update(self, i, val):
        n = self.l + i
        self.tree[n] = val
        while n > 1:
            self.tree[n >> 1] = self.tree[n] + self.tree[n ^ 1]
            n >>= 1

    def sumRange(self, i, j):
        m = self.l + i
        n = self.l + j
        res = 0
        while m <= n:
            if m & 1:
                res += self.tree[m]
                m += 1
            m >>= 1
            if n & 1 == 0:
                res += self.tree[n]
                n -= 1
            n >>= 1
        return res

Fenwicktree python

class FenwickTree:
    def __init__(self,n):
        self._sums = [0 for _ in range(n+1)]

    def update(self,i,delta):
        while i < len(self._sums):
            self._sums[i] += delta
            i += i & -i
    
    def query(self,i):
        s = 0
        while i > 0:
            s += self._sums[i]
            i -= i & -i
        return s

class NumArray:

    def __init__(self, nums: List[int]):
        self._nums = nums
        self._tree = FenwickTree(len(nums))
        for i in range(len(nums)):
            self._tree.update(i+1,nums[i])

    def update(self, i: int, val: int) -> None:
        self._tree.update(i+1,val-self._nums[i])
        self._nums[i] = val

    def sumRange(self, i: int, j: int) -> int:
        return self._tree.query(j+1)-self._tree.query(i)

class Node:
    def __init__(self, val):
        self.val = val
        self.left = None
        self.right = None

class NumArray:

    def buildTree(self, nums):
        l = len(nums)
        if l==0:
            return None
        root = Node(nums[0])
        if l==1:
            return root
        root.left = self.buildTree(nums[0:l//2])
        root.right = self.buildTree(nums[l//2:])
        root.val = root.left.val + root.right.val
        return root

    def updateTree(self, new_val, i, node, a, b):
        #print(a,b)
        if i<a or i>b:
            return
        if a==b:
            delta = new_val - node.val
            node.val = new_val
            return delta
        mid = (a+b+1)//2
        if i<mid:
            delta = self.updateTree(new_val, i, node.left, a, mid-1)
        else:
            delta = self.updateTree(new_val, i, node.right, mid, b)
        #print(delta)
        node.val += delta
        return delta
        
    def sumTree(self, i, j, a, b, node):
        #print(a, b)
        if i==a and j==b-1 or a+1==b:
            return node.val

        mid = (a+b)//2
        if i<mid:
            left_sum = self.sumTree(i, j, a, mid, node.left)
        else:
            left_sum = 0
        if j>=mid:
            right_sum = self.sumTree(i, j, mid, b, node.right)
        else:
            right_sum = 0
        return left_sum + right_sum

    def printTree(self):
        queue = [self.tree]
        while queue:
            new_queue = []
            row = ""
            for node in queue:
                if node:
                    row += str(node.val) + " "
                    new_queue.append(node.left)
                    new_queue.append(node.right)
                else:
                    row += " "
            print(row)
            queue = new_queue

    def __init__(self, nums: List[int]):
        self.l = len(nums)
        self.tree = self.buildTree(nums)


    def update(self, i: int, val: int) -> None:
        #self.printTree()
        self.updateTree(val, i, self.tree, 0, self.l-1)

    def sumRange(self, i: int, j: int) -> int:
        #self.printTree()
        res = self.sumTree(i, j, 0, self.l, self.tree)
        #print(res)
        return res

默默的放个线段树

class NumArray {
private:
    struct SegmentTree {
        int l, r;
        int dat;
    };
public:
    vector<SegmentTree> t;
    void build(int p, int l, int r, vector<int> &v, vector<SegmentTree> &t) {
        t[p].l = l, t[p].r = r;
        if (l == r) {
            t[p].dat = v[l - 1];
            return;
        }
        int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;
        build(p * 2, l, mid, v, t);
        build(p * 2 + 1, mid + 1, r, v, t);
        t[p].dat = t[p * 2].dat + t[p * 2 + 1].dat;
    }
    
    void change(int p, int x, int v, vector<SegmentTree> &t) {
        if(t[p].l == t[p].r) {
            t[p].dat = v;
            return;
        }
        int mid = (t[p].l + t[p].r) / 2;
        if (x <= mid)
            change(p * 2, x, v, t);
        else
            change(p * 2 + 1, x, v, t);
        t[p].dat = t[p * 2].dat + t[p * 2 + 1].dat;
    }
    
    int ask(int p, int l, int r, vector<SegmentTree> &t) {
        if (l <= t[p].l && r >= t[p].r)
            return t[p].dat;
        int mid = (t[p].l + t[p].r) / 2;
        int val = 0;
        if (l <= mid) {
            val = val + ask(p * 2, l, r, t);
        }
        if (r > mid) {
            val = val + ask(p * 2 + 1, l, r, t);
        }
        return val;
    }
    
    NumArray(vector<int>& nums) {
        int n = nums.size();
        if (n < 1) return;
        vector<SegmentTree> tmp(4 * n);
        t = tmp;
        build(1, 1, n, nums, t);
    }
    
    void update(int i, int val) {
        change(1, i + 1, val, t);
    }

    int sumRange(int i, int j) {
        return ask(1, i + 1, j + 1, t);
    }
};

9 天前

Java题解 简单明了

区间修改+查询 -> 线段树求解

class NumArray {

    int[] tree;
    int index, length;
    public NumArray(int[] nums) {

        tree = new int[nums.length * 4 + 1];
        index = 0;
        length = nums.length;
        
        if (length != 0)
            buildTree(nums, 1, 1, length);
    }


    public void buildTree(int[] nums, int node, int l, int r) {

        // 叶子结点
        if (l == r) {
            tree[node] = nums[index++];
            return;
        }

        int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;
        buildTree(nums, 2 * node, l, mid);
        buildTree(nums, 2 * node + 1, mid + 1, r);
        tree[node] = tree[node * 2] + tree[node * 2 + 1];
    }

    public void update(int i, int val) {

        update(i + 1, val, 1, 1, length);
    }

    public void update(int i, int val, int node, int l, int r) {

        // 找到更新
        if (l == r) {
            tree[node] = val;
            return;
        }

        int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;
        if (i <= mid)
            update(i, val, node * 2, l, mid);
        else
            update(i, val, node * 2 + 1, mid + 1, r);
        // 更新值
        tree[node] = tree[node * 2] + tree[node * 2 + 1];
    }

    public int sumRange(int i, int j) {

        return sumRange(i + 1, j + 1, 1, 1, length);
    }

    public int sumRange(int i, int j, int node, int l, int r) {

        if (i <= l && j >= r)
            return tree[node];

        int mid = l + (r - l) / 2;
        int sum = 0;

        if (mid >= i)
            sum += sumRange(i, j, node * 2, l, mid);
        if (j > mid)
            sum += sumRange(i, j, node * 2 + 1, mid + 1, r);

        return sum;
    }
}

最简单的解决办法

class NumArray {
    private int[] sum;
    private int[] data;

    public NumArray(int[] nums) {
        data=new int[nums.length];
        for (int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
            data[i]=nums[i];
        }
        sum=new int[nums.length+1];
        sum[0]=0;
        for (int i=1;i<sum.length;i++){
            sum[i]=sum[i-1]+nums[i-1];
        }
    }

    public void update(int i, int val) {
        data[i]=val;
        for(int j=i+1;j<sum.length;j++){
            sum[j]=sum[j-1]+data[j-1];
        }
    }

    public int sumRange(int i, int j) {
        return sum[j+1]-sum[i];
    }
}

python

class IndexTree(object):
    def __init__(self,nums):
        n = len(nums)
        sum = [0] * (n+1)
        for i in range(1,n+1):
            sum[i] = sum[i-1] + nums[i-1]
        self.sum = [0] * (n+1)
        for i in range(1,n+1):
            self.sum[i] = sum[i] - sum[i-(i&-i)]
        
        
    def getSum(self,i):
        res = 0
        while i != 0:
            res += self.sum[i]
            i -= (i & -i)
        return res
    
    def update(self,i,val):
        n = len(self.sum) - 1
        while i <= n:
            self.sum[i] += val
            i += (i & -i)
            
class NumArray:

    def __init__(self, nums: 'List[int]'):
        self.tree = IndexTree(nums)
        self.nums = nums
        

    def update(self, i: 'int', val: 'int') -> 'None':
        diff = val - self.nums[i]
        self.nums[i] = val
        self.tree.update(i+1,diff)
        

    def sumRange(self, i: 'int', j: 'int') -> 'int':
        return self.tree.getSum(j+1) - self.tree.getSum(i)


        
# Your NumArray object will be instantiated and called as such:
# obj = NumArray(nums)
# obj.update(i,val)
# param_2 = obj.sumRange(i,j)```

int build(int*, int, int, int, int*);
int query(int*, int, int, int, int, int);

typedef struct {
    int* nums;
    int* trees;
    int size;
    int (*build)(int*, int, int, int, int*);
    int (*query)(int*, int, int, int, int, int);
    void (*update)(int*, int, int, int, int, int);
} NumArray;

NumArray* numArrayCreate(int* nums, int numsSize) {
    int* trees = (int*)malloc(sizeof(int*) * numsSize * 4);
    NumArray* obj = (NumArray*)malloc(sizeof(NumArray));
    obj->trees = trees;
    obj->nums = nums, 
    obj->size = numsSize;
    obj->build = build;
    obj->query = query;
    obj->update = update;
    
    if(numsSize == 0){
        return obj;
    }
    
    obj->build(obj->trees, 0, 0, obj->size - 1, obj->nums);
    return obj;
}

void numArrayUpdate(NumArray* obj, int i, int val) {
    obj->update(obj->trees, 0, 0, obj->size - 1, i, val - obj->nums[i]);
    obj->nums[i] = val;
}

int numArraySumRange(NumArray* obj, int i, int j) {
    return obj->query(obj->trees, 0, 0, obj->size - 1, i, j);
}

void numArrayFree(NumArray* obj) {
    free(obj->trees);
    free(obj);
}


int query(int* trees, int index, int l, int r, int i, int j){
    if(i == l && j == r){
        return trees[index];
    }
    
    int m = l + (r - l) / 2;
    if(j <= m){
        return query(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, i, j);
    }
    if(i > m){
        return query(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, i, j);
    }
    
    int sumLeft = query(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, i, m);
    int sumRight = query(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, m + 1, j);
    
    return sumLeft + sumRight;
}

void update(int* trees, int index, int l, int r, int i, int diff){
    if(l == r){
        trees[index] += diff;
        return ;
    }
    
    trees[index] += diff;
    int m = l + (r - l) / 2;
    if(i <= m){
        update(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, i, diff);
    }else{
        update(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, i, diff);
    }
}

int build(int* trees, int index, int l, int r, int* nums){
    if(l == r){
        return trees[index] = nums[l];
    }
    
    int m = l + (r - l) / 2;
    build(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, nums);
    build(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, nums);
    
    int sumLeft = build(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, nums);
    int sumRight = build(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, nums);
    
    return trees[index] = sumLeft + sumRight;
}

因为递归操作比较耗时，所以优化了下代码，更新操作可以很容易优化为迭代。对于构建函数，假如是一个满二叉树，那么我们就可以从叶子节点一步步往根节点计算出结果（trees[i] = trees[i * 2 + 1] + trees[i * 2 + 2];）。对于某个数组长度，我们可以延长数组长度为大于原数组长度的2的n次方的最小值，对于大于原数组长度的值，全部置为0即可。对于测试用例，优化完的代码为28ms，未优化为1800多ms。

void build(int*, int, int*, int);
int query(int*, int, int, int, int, int);
void update(int*, int, int, int, int, int);


typedef struct {
    int* nums;
    int* trees;
    int size;
    void (*build)(int*, int, int*, int);
    int (*query)(int*, int, int, int, int, int);
    void (*update)(int*, int, int, int, int, int);
} NumArray;

NumArray* numArrayCreate(int* nums, int numsSize) {
    int size = 1;
    while(size < numsSize){
        size <<= 1;
    }
    
    int* trees = (int*)malloc(sizeof(int*) * size * 2);//满二叉树
    NumArray* obj = (NumArray*)malloc(sizeof(NumArray));
    obj->trees = trees;
    obj->nums = nums, 
    obj->size = size;
    obj->build = build;
    obj->query = query;
    obj->update = update;
    
    if(numsSize == 0){
        return obj;
    }
    
    obj->build(obj->trees, obj->size * 2 - 1, obj->nums, numsSize);
    return obj;
}

void numArrayUpdate(NumArray* obj, int i, int val) {
    obj->update(obj->trees, 0, 0, obj->size - 1, i, val - obj->nums[i]);
    obj->nums[i] = val;
}

int numArraySumRange(NumArray* obj, int i, int j) {
    return obj->query(obj->trees, 0, 0, obj->size - 1, i, j);
}

void numArrayFree(NumArray* obj) {
    free(obj->trees);
    free(obj);
}


int query(int* trees, int index, int l, int r, int i, int j){
    if(i == l && j == r){
        return trees[index];
    }
    
    int m = l + (r - l) / 2;
    if(j <= m){
        return query(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, i, j);
    }else if(i > m){
        return query(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, i, j);
    }else{
        return query(trees, index * 2 + 1, l, m, i, m) + query(trees, index * 2 + 2, m + 1, r, m + 1, j);
    }
}

void update(int* trees, int index, int l, int r, int i, int diff){
    trees[index] += diff;
    while(l < r){
        int m = l + (r - l) / 2;
        if(i <= m){
            index = index * 2 + 1;
            r = m;
        }else{
            index = index * 2 + 2;
            l = m + 1;
        }
        trees[index] += diff;
    }
}

void build(int* trees, int treesSize, int* nums, int numsSize){
    int j = treesSize, i = j / 2, k = 0;
    while(i < j){//初始化叶子节点
        if(k < numsSize){
            trees[i] = nums[k++];
        }else{
            trees[i] = 0;
        }
        i++;
    }
    
    while(j > 0){//求解父节点
        j /= 2;
        i = j / 2;
        while(i < j){
            trees[i] = trees[i * 2 + 1] + trees[i * 2 + 2];
            i++;
        }
    }
}

class NumArray {
public:
    NumArray(vector<int>& nums) {
        res = nums;
    }
    
    void update(int i, int val) {
        res[i] = val;
    }
    
    int sumRange(int i, int j) {
        int total = 0;
        for(int k = i;k <= j;k++)
        {
            total += res[k];
        }
        return total;
    }
private:
    vector<int> res;
};
